<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jelena Jhang — Character File No.001</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #F0EDE8;
            --navy: #1E3560;
            --navy-light: #2D4A7A;
            --gold: #C4973A;
            --gold-light: #E8D4A0;
            --light-bg: #E8EDF5;
            --divider: #D0C8BE;
            --warm-gray: #8A8070;
            --text-dark: #2C2825;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --accent-green: #2D6A4A;
            --accent-purple: #5A3A7A;
            --accent-red: #8A2A2A;
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #dcd7cf;
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .card-container {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            width: 1000px;
            max-width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            border: 3px solid var(--navy);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Border Details */
        .card-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 6px;
            left: 6px;
            right: 6px;
            bottom: 6px;
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .dot {
            position: absolute;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background-color: var(--gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 11;
        }
        .dot.tl { top: 3px; left: 3px; }
        .dot.tr { top: 3px; right: 3px; }
        .dot.bl { bottom: 3px; left: 3px; }
        .dot.br { bottom: 3px; right: 3px; }

        /* Grid Pattern */
        .grid-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(to right, #E8E4DC 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(to bottom, #E8E4DC 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 36px 36px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: var(--navy);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 30px 48px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold);
        }

        .header-top {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .id-num {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7A99CC;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .tags {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .tags span {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #5577AA;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #AABBD0;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .motto {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #AABBD0;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        main {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 420px 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 40px 48px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: var(--gold);
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            height: 2px;
            background-color: var(--navy-light);
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* Left Column */
        .profile-card {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .avatar-container {
            width: 160px;
            height: 200px;
            border: 3px solid var(--navy);
            background-color: var(--gold-light);
            position: relative;
            padding: 2px;
        }

        .avatar-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .profile-info h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 32px;
            color: var(--navy);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .role-title {
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .location {
            color: var(--warm-gray);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .achievement {
            color: var(--navy-light);
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .mini-badges {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .mini-badge {
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        /* Profile List */
        .profile-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .profile-list li {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
        }

        .profile-list .label {
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: 700;
            width: 80px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        /* Stats */
        .stat-item {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .stat-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .stat-grade {
            background-color: var(--navy);
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 1px 6px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        .stat-bar-bg {
            height: 10px;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .stat-bar-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background-color: var(--navy-light);
            width: 0;
            transition: width 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.1, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .stat-bar-tip {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 8px;
        }

        .stat-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--warm-gray);
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* Right Column */
        .backstory p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .special-ability {
            background-color: var(--navy);
            border-left: 6px solid var(--gold);
            padding: 24px;
            color: var(--white);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .ability-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .ability-desc {
            color: #AABBD0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .future-quest {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .future-quest blockquote {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 26px;
            color: var(--navy);
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.4;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--gold);
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .keyword-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .keyword-tag {
            border: 1px solid var(--navy-light);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--navy-light);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .keyword-tag:hover {
            background-color: var(--navy-light);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--divider);
            color: var(--warm-gray);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--navy);
            color: #7A99CC;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--gold);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            main {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .card-container {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card-container">
        <div class="dot tl"></div>
        <div class="dot tr"></div>
        <div class="dot bl"></div>
        <div class="dot br"></div>
        <div class="grid-overlay"></div>

        <header>
            <div class="header-top">
                <div class="id-num">CHARACTER FILE — No. 001</div>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span>Logistics</span>
                    <span>Japanese</span>
                    <span>AI Tools</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h1>Jelena Jhang</h1>
            <p class="motto">用語言理解世界，用工具讓工作更好。</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <!-- Left Side -->
            <div class="left-col">
                <section class="profile-card">
                    <div class="avatar-container">
                        <img id="avatar" src="" alt="Jelena Jhang Profile">
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-info">
                        <h2>張 姵 涵</h2>
                        <div class="role-title">Logistics<br>Coordinator</div>
                        <div class="location">Taichung, Taiwan</div>
                        <div class="achievement">JLPT N1 ★ 2025</div>
                        <div class="mini-badges">
                            <div class="mini-badge" style="background-color: var(--gold);">S 日語</div>
                            <div class="mini-badge" style="background-color: var(--accent-green);">A 物流</div>
                            <div class="mini-badge" style="background-color: var(--navy-light);">A 溝通</div>
                            <div class="mini-badge" style="background-color: var(--accent-purple);">A 文件</div>
                            <div class="mini-badge" style="background-color: var(--accent-red);">A+ 解決</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <div class="section-title">PROFILE</div>
                    <ul class="profile-list">
                        <li><span class="label">Role</span> 物流業務助理（在職 3 年）</li>
                        <li><span class="label">Lang</span> 中文 / 日文 N1 / English</li>
                        <li><span class="label">Study</span> 福岡短期交換研修</li>
                        <li><span class="label">Tools</span> LINE Bot / AI辨識 / GAS</li>
                        <li><span class="label">Type</span> 細心・溫柔・負責・耐心</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <div class="section-title">ABILITY STATS</div>
                    
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-header">
                            <span class="stat-label">日語能力</span>
                            <span class="stat-grade" style="background-color: var(--gold);">S</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-bar-bg">
                            <div class="stat-bar-fill" data-progress="96%" style="background-color: var(--navy-light);"></div>
                            <div class="stat-bar-tip" style="right: 4%; background-color: var(--gold);"></div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="stat-note">JLPT N1・福岡研修・日商書信</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-header">
                            <span class="stat-label">物流實務</span>
                            <span class="stat-grade" style="background-color: var(--accent-green);">A</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-bar-bg">
                            <div class="stat-bar-fill" data-progress="85%" style="background-color: var(--navy-light);"></div>
                            <div class="stat-bar-tip" style="right: 15%; background-color: var(--accent-green);"></div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="stat-note">訂單庫存交期協調 3yr+</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-header">
                            <span class="stat-label">客戶溝通</span>
                            <span class="stat-grade" style="background-color: var(--navy-light);">A</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-bar-bg">
                            <div class="stat-bar-fill" data-progress="90%" style="background-color: var(--navy-light);"></div>
                            <div class="stat-bar-tip" style="right: 10%; background-color: var(--navy-light);"></div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="stat-note">三語往來・細心溝通</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-header">
                            <span class="stat-label">文件整理</span>
                            <span class="stat-grade" style="background-color: var(--accent-purple);">A</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-bar-bg">
                            <div class="stat-bar-fill" data-progress="88%" style="background-color: var(--navy-light);"></div>
                            <div class="stat-bar-tip" style="right: 12%; background-color: var(--accent-purple);"></div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="stat-note">跨語言文件・帳單追蹤</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-header">
                            <span class="stat-label">解決問題</span>
                            <span class="stat-grade" style="background-color: var(--accent-red);">A+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-bar-bg">
                            <div class="stat-bar-fill" data-progress="92%" style="background-color: var(--navy-light);"></div>
                            <div class="stat-bar-tip" style="right: 8%; background-color: var(--accent-red);"></div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="stat-note">自製 3 個數位工具</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Side -->
            <div class="right-col">
                <section class="backstory">
                    <div class="section-title">BACKSTORY</div>
                    <p>她的日文不是為了考試而學的。大學三年級，因為喜歡日劇和動漫，開始一句一句地拆解這個語言。靠自學打底，畢業前取得 N2，赴日本福岡短期交換研修一個月，在全日文環境中獨立生活、上課、溝通——語感在那段時間變得更自然、更直覺。</p>
                    <p>進入職場後，日文成了工作裡真實的工具：承接日本廠商的詢報價、交期確認、異常說明等書信往來；在涉及物流的會議場合，能以日文適時補充說明，確保資訊不因語言落差而失真；更擅長在會後整理重點、追蹤後續，讓溝通真正推進事情進展。2025 年，JLPT N1 正式合格。</p>
                    <p>她習慣把眼睛放在「哪裡不順」。庫存查詢繁瑣→做了 LINE Bot；報價換算複雜→做了計算器；訂單格式混亂→開發 AI 辨識系統。這些工具不是為了展示技術，而是從真實的麻煩長出來的解法。她不只是執行工作的人，也是會主動讓工作變得更好的人。</p>
                </section>

                <section class="special-ability">
                    <div class="ability-name">語言力 × 實務力 × 自製工具力</div>
                    <div class="ability-desc">遇到問題不只回報，而是想辦法解決它。</div>
                </section>

                <section class="future-quest">
                    <div class="section-title">FUTURE QUEST</div>
                    <blockquote>
                        找到一個讓語言發光、讓細心被看見的地方，在穩定中持續累積、慢慢變強。
                    </blockquote>
                    <div class="keyword-tags">
                        <div class="keyword-tag">JLPT N1</div>
                        <div class="keyword-tag">物流3年</div>
                        <div class="keyword-tag">福岡研修</div>
                        <div class="keyword-tag">日商往來</div>
                        <div class="keyword-tag">AI工具</div>
                        <div class="keyword-tag">台中在地</div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <div class="contact-info">
                    jelena19961122@gmail.com   ·   0985-496781
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer>
            Jelena Jhang  ·  Character File 2025  ·  Taichung, Taiwan
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Set profile photo path
        document.getElementById('avatar').src = 'character.png';

        // Animate progress bars on load
        window.addEventListener('load', () => {
            const bars = document.querySelectorAll('.stat-bar-fill');
            bars.forEach(bar => {
                const progress = bar.getAttribute('data-progress');
                setTimeout(() => {
                    bar.style.width = progress;
                }, 400);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
